; Coverage test for post.cc (get_cost), (get_price):
; Exercise get_has_cost, get_cost, and get_price with costs and without.

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Broker    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/15 Salary
    Income:Salary   $-5000.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Assets:Broker --format "%(has_cost) %(cost) %(price)\n"
true $1500.00 $1500.00
end test
